{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2989780, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我国高等教育的天花板，清华，竟然有超过5个人信地平论。大为震撼", "timestamp": 1637377147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2989795, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989780, "tag": null, "text": "缓缓打出一个 ？", "timestamp": 1637377260, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2989803, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "*******", "timestamp": 1637377340, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2989829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看来正经投票的人还是比较多", "timestamp": 1637377570, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2989937, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本人驽钝，不是杠，认真求教\n虽然从小我们就知道地球是一个椭球 我们生活的所谓平地只是因为人相对于这个球太小了所以感受不到弧度\n但我们之中罕有人亲自做过环球旅行，更没有人乘坐宇宙飞船上天观察\n那么如何证明我们自己不是处在一个“被欺骗为地球不是平的”的楚门的世界呢？\n(可能有些反智，但我真的很驽钝，希望能得到有力的反驳，请勿人身攻击)", "timestamp": 1637378446, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2989986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 多学物理，请", "timestamp": 1637378770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2989995, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 坐飞机绕地球一圈", "timestamp": 1637378817, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 很多生活中能观察到的现象（如昼夜交替等）都可以佐证地球是个（椭）球体，也就是说至少我可以说地球是（椭）球体的置信度可以非常高", "timestamp": 1637378859, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990007, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "就算你做不了环球旅行，你也可以做一个小小的傅科摆实验", "timestamp": 1637378880, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 看漏水漩涡其实就行了", "timestamp": 1637378993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990038, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 海边的桅杆，古希腊的例子。托勒密王朝时代就有人能通过一年时间中影子长度的变化计算出地球的弧度。另外，你可以找校内的物理实验室，用装置亲自验证万有引力定律，那么就能自然的推理引力定律下，一个自转的大质量物体在空间中的稳定形态：两极略扁的椭球形。", "timestamp": 1637379061, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990057, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2990038, "tag": null, "text": "笑死了，大家选有可能也就图一乐，你们还真辩论起来了", "timestamp": 1637379147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我国高等教育的天花板，清华，竟然有超过5个人信树洞的投票结果。大为震撼", "timestamp": 1637379386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我国高等教育的天花板，清华，竟然有超过5个人信树洞的投票结果。大为震撼", "timestamp": 1637379487, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2990057, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 确实，是我鲁莽了。虽然真的有认真讨论起占星术和地平论合理性的人，我相信那也只是少数了。", "timestamp": 1637379646, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2990838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2989937, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: https://www.zhihu.com/answer/159769569", "timestamp": 1637384555, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2991023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2990838, "tag": null, "text": "我还怀疑我生活在计算机模拟的世界呢，你会发现总需要你承认一些事实你才能推导下去。学科研究的系统里往往默认一些事实，但你放在随便一个环境下，不约定事实然后强加自己认为的事实到所有人对这个环境的认识中是不是多少流氓了点。", "timestamp": 1637385745, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2991985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "\"平”不是形容词，是名词，当然是平的", "timestamp": 1637394787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2992099, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2991985, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 万物皆可zzxg", "timestamp": 1637395721, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2992313, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2991985, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 草", "timestamp": 1637397624, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2995230, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2991985, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 草", "timestamp": 1637422341, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2995624, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "认识论，是这个词吗。人必须假设一些事实才行。比如说缸中之脑，如何验证你不是一个被控制的大脑，你的所有感受都是被各种计算机和神经技术模拟出来的？答案是没有办法完全证明。但是，如果你问我，你相信科学吗，你能证明自己不是缸中之脑吗，我会说：我不能完全证明，但这不会影响我的行动。我该吃吃该喝喝，该写实验报告处理nt数据就处理。", "timestamp": 1637425861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2995673, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "必须要区分，理论上的思考对人的现实活动有没有意义。我认为没法证明地球是圆的，但基于我的科学素养，如果有人认真地宣传地平说我会觉得他多少沾点", "timestamp": 1637426063, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2996867, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Queen", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2991985, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 正确的😇", "timestamp": 1637458585, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997354, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Richard", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "地球不是平的还能是媛的？", "timestamp": 1637464240, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997405, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": 2997354, "tag": null, "text": "Re Richard: 好！\n", "timestamp": 1637464765, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3014698, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 566392, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢大家，受教了", "timestamp": 1637649715, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 18, "pid": 566392, "reply": 27, "tag": null, "text": "#566303\n原洞让我大受震撼，开一个极端些的投票\n你觉得地球可能是平的吗？", "timestamp": 1637376870, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637649715, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"♀，有可能": 59, "♀，不可能": 125, "♂，有可能": 132, "♂，不可能": 285}, "vote_options": ["♀，有可能", "♀，不可能", "♂，有可能", "♂，不可能"]}}}